at%20ensues%20for%20the%20yellowish-green%20hues%20to%20transform%20into%20its%20ripe%20golden-orange%20form.%20And%20no%20one%20questions%20the%20long%20queues%20outside%20popular%20Gujarati%20joints%20whose%20%3Cem%3Eaamras%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20of%20sweet%20mango%20pulp%20served%20with%20deep-fried%20flatbread)%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20die%20for%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20regulars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20juicy%20fact%20that%20summers%20in%20India%20are%20incomplete%20without%20mango%20dominating%20our%20homes%20and%20palates.%20This%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise.%20Indians%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F57267%2Fmango-national-fruit-of-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivating%20mangoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20and%20till%20today%2C%20the%20love%20for%20the%20fruit%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20waned%20even%20one%20bit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Alphonso%20continues%20to%20hold%20its%20status%20as%20a%20cult%20favourite%20for%20its%20vibrant%20sweetness%20and%20distinct%20flavour%2C%20there%20are%20hundreds%2C%20if%20not%20thousands%20of%20varieties%20that%20dot%20the%20landscape%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20mango%20cultivation.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20lesser-known%20varieties%20make%20an%20appearance%20in%20chutneys%2C%20pickles%20and%20the%20like%2C%20lending%20them%20their%20citrusy%20flavour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20if%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20got%20your%20stock%20of%20mangoes%20yet%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20a%20suggestion%3A%20why%20not%20get%20them%20delivered%20to%20you%20straight%20from%20a%20farm%3F%20We%E2%80%99ve%20put%20together%20a%20list%20of%20people%2C%20startups%20and%20local%20platforms%20that%20are%20bringing%20the%20sweetness%20of%20the%20mango%20from%20the%20tree%20to%20your%20plate.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Athalya%20Vandh