e%2C%20Now%20They%20Speak%20For%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Banswara%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20the%20Congress%20found%20itself%20campaigning%20against%20its%20own%20candidate.%20The%20party%20had%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party's%20(BAP)%20Rajkumar%20Roat%2C%20while%20the%20Congress'%20Arvind%20Damor%2C%20who%20had%20already%20filed%20his%20nomination%2C%20refused%20to%20withdraw%2C%20remaining%20in%20the%20fray%20as%20a%20Congress%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELack%20Of%20Control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incidents%20in%20Indore%2C%20Surat%2C%20and%20Banswara%20are%20unprecedented%20for%20any%20party.%20The%20recent%20incidents%20indicate%20a%20complete%20lack%20of%20planning%20and%20control%20within%20the%20Congress%20as%20well%20as%20deficiencies%20in%20its%20candidate%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Congress's%20candidate%2C%20Rohan%20Gupta%2C%20returned%20his%20ticket%20from%20Ahmedabad%20East%2C%20citing%20his%20father's%20illness%2C%20only%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20after%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20experienced%20a%20significant%20exodus%20of%20leaders%2C%20including%20big%20names%20like%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20and%20Sunil%20Jakhar.%20According%20to%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%2C%20out%20of%20the%20405%20MLAs%20who%20quit%20and%20switched%20parties%20from%202016-2020%2C%20as%20many%20as%20170%20-%20that%20is%2C%2042%25%20-%20were%20from%20the%20Congress.%20In%20contrast%2C%20only%204.4%25%20-%20or%20just%2018%20-%20BJP%20legislators%20jumped%20ship%20in%20this%20period.%20Out%20of%20the%2012%20Lok%20Sabha%20members%20who%20switched%20parties%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20five%20were%20from%20the%20BJP.%20In%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20out%20of%20the%2017%20who%20quit%2C%20seven%20were%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20ADR%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeaders%20With%20Questionable%20Loyalties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20much%20has%20been%20said%20about%20the%20human%20resource%20issues%20facing%20Congress%20and%20its%20inability%20to%20retain%20talent%2C%20very%20little%20has%20been%20discussed%20about%20the%20leaders%20with%20questionable%20loyalties%20holding%20a%20place%20in%20the%20grand%20old%20party.%20With%20these%20incidents%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20ascertain%20how%20many%20of%20the%20declared%20Congress%20candidates%20are%20truly%20committed%20to%20the%20party%20and%20how%20many%20have%20a%20secret%20pact%20with%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20remarks%20of%20Sam%20Pitroda%20on%20inheritance%20tax%20have%20also%20sparked%20a%20row.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20known%20offender%20of%20sorts.%20In%20May%202019%2C%20Pitroda%2C%20when%20questioned%20on%20the%201984%20anti-Sikh%20riots%2C%20set%20off%20a%20storm%20with%20his%20rather%20insensitive%20remarks.%20In%20June%202023%2C%20his%20remark%20that%20temples%20were%20not%20going%20to%20solve%20India's%20problems%20of%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%2C%20education%2C%20and%20health%2C%20again%20sparked%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-says-like-dinosaurs-congress-will-be-extinct-in-few-years-5425354%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%20Rajnath%20Singh%20Says%20%26quot%3BLike%20Dinosaurs%2C%20Congress%20Will%20Be%20Extinct%20In%20Few%20Years%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20state%20that%20faced%20elections%20in%202022%2C%20the%20main%20criterion%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20Congress%20candidates%20was%20bizarre%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20The%20state%20leadership%20asked%20surveyors%20to%20recommend%20candidates%20who%20would%20not%20switch%20over%20to%20the%20BJP.%20How%20could%20anyone%20do%20this%3F%20How%20could%20pollsters%20find%20out%20what%20was%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20candidates%20or%20whether%20they%20could%20have%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20later%3F%20In%20the%20same%20state%2C%20when%20pollsters%20were%20tracking%20weekly%20vote%20share%20movements%20across%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20a%20few%20days%20closer%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20began%20leading%20on%20a%20few%20seats%20it%20had%20been%20trailing%20in%20earlier.%20A%20detailed%20inquiry%20suggested%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20put%20up%20weak%20candidates%20against%20these%20Congress%20nominees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EScoring%20Self-Goals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20like%20Pitroda%20and%20many%20others%20keep%20on%20scoring%20self-goals.%20Before%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20half%20a%20dozen%20Congress%20candidates%20pulled%20out%20after%20the%20party%20officially%20announced%20their%20names%2C%20damaging%20its%20chances%20even%20before%20the%20contest%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternal%20squabbles%20are%20one%20of%20the%20key%20diseases%20plaguing%20the%20Congress%20today.%20Many%20leaders%20are%20alleged%20to%20have%20close%20connections%20with%20rival%20parties%20and%20their%20loyalty%20is%20questionable.%20The%20recent%20instances%20indicate%20just%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20hoping%20to%20avoid%20such%20faux%20pas%20in%20the%20remaining%20phases.%20But%20the%20BJP%20would%20try%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20pattern%20repeats%20as%20it%20helps%20build%20a%20narrative%20of%20which%20way%20the%20wind%20is%20blowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714480380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fl4nvcoak_lrc_160x120_17_December_2