dra%20Modi%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20can%20never%20think%20small.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20can%20never%20think%20small%2C%20Jab%20Bhagwan%20ne%20mujhe%20manufacture%20kiya%20(when%20God%20manufactured%20me)%2C%20he%20didn't%20put%20the%20'small'%20chip%2C%20but%20only%20the%20big%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Latur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Olympics%2C%20Paralympics%2C%20Asian%20Games%2C%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20and%20University%20Games%2C%20Indian%20players%20are%20breaking%20decades-old%20records.%20This%20confidence%20among%20Indian%20citizens%20will%20take%20us%20towards%20a%20developed%20India.%20It%20is%20my%20dream%20to%20host%20the%202029%20Youth%20Olympics%20in%20India.%20it%20is%20my%20dream%20that%20the%202036%20Olympics%20be%20held%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20country%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20earlier%20regular%20announcements%20were%20made%20warning%20of%20unattended%20objects%2C%20while%20today%20India%20is%20able%20to%20safeguard%20its%20border%20strongly.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20took%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20Congress%20party%20referring%20to%20the%2026%2F11%20terror%20attacks%20and%20said%20earlier%20the%20government%20was%20only%20able%20to%20send%20the%20dossier%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20while%20today%20it%20can%20kill%20its%20enemies%20inside%20their%20own%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%202014%2C%20there%20would%20be%20announcements%20at%20railways%20stations%2C%20fares%20and%20crowded%20places%20warning%20of%20unattended%20objects...In%20the%20whole%20country%2C%2024%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20such%20warnings%20were%20issued%20in%20important%20places...Where%20did%20these%20unattended%20objects%20disappear%20after%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister%3F%20At%20that%20time%2C%20newspapers%20had%20headlines%20informing%20about%20bomb%20blasts%20every%20other%20day%20and%20police%20were%20not%20equipped%20to%20counter%20advanced%20threats.%20Today%2C%20India%20is%20known%20for%20giving%20a%20strong%20reply%20to%20those%20looking%20at%20our%20borders%20with%20ill%20intentions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20there%20were%20headlines%20that%20India%20sent%20a%20new%20dossier%20(documents)%20to%20Pakistan%20in%20connection%20with%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks.%20Today%2C%20India%20no%20longer%20sends%20dossier%2C%20ghar%20mein%20ghus%20kar%20maarta%20hai%20(kills%20enemies%20inside%20their%20houses)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20attacked%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20alleging%20that%20the%20alliance%20is%20planning%20to%20have%20one%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20each%20year%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20country%20can't%20be%20thrown%20into%20such%20'uncertainty'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20talk%20about%20'Ek%20Bharat%20Shrestha%20Bharat'%2C%20the%20'shehzada'%20of%20Congress%20catches%20fever.%20They%20ask%20why%20I%20talk%20about%20one%20India.%20Those%20who%20view%20India%20in%20divisions%2C%20also%20want%20to%20divide%20the%20Prime%20Ministerial%20post.%20Their%20plan%20of%20have%20five%20PMs%20in%20five%20years%2C%20which%20means%20looting%20the%20country%20in%20turns.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%2C%20should%20such%20people%20be%20given%20even%20the%20slightest%20of%20chance%3F%20Can%20we%20throw%20our%20country%20into%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20current%20period%20of%20global%20turbulence%3F%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20attacked%20the%20Congress%20party%20over%20its%20manifesto%20and%20asked%20people%20if%20they%20would%20allow%20the%20party%20to%20%26quot%3Bloot%26quot%3B%20their%20hard-earned%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20made%20a%20dangerous%20plan%2C%20they%20will%20carry%20an%20x-ray%20of%20your%20properties%2C%20then%20seize%20it%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20their%20vote%20bank.%20Will%20you%20allow%20Congress%20to%20loot%20your%20property%3F%20Congress%20has%20set%20its%20eagle%20eyes%20on%20your%20wealth%2C%20will%20you%20allow%20the%20'panja'%20(veiled%20attack%20at%20Congress'%20hand%20symbol)%20to%20loot%20your%20properties%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20sends%2048%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20polling%20in%20the%20state%20is%20being%20held%20across%20five%20phases.%20Voting%20in%2013%20seats%20has%20already%20concluded%20in%2013%20out%20of%20the%2048%20seats.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20is%20scheduled%20for%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20BJP%20won%2023%20out%20of%2048%20seats%2C%20while%20its%20NDA%20ally%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20won%2018%20seats.%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20and%20Congress%20could%20only%20win%20four%20and%20one%20seat%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714480140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fqkjv54a8_pm-modi-1200_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-god-made-me-pm-modi-on-why-he-cant-think-small-5557535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elaborating%20on%20his%20'ambitious'%20vision%20for%20the%20country%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20can%20never%20think%20small.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-god-made-me-pm-modi-on-why-he-cant-think-small-5557535%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-god-made-me-pm-modi-on-why-he-cant-think-small-5557535%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-g