e%20of%20the%20people%2C%20we%20built%20it.%20We'll%20never%20let%20it%20erase%2C%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20labourers%20will%20never%20let%20it%20happen.%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20planning%20to%20change%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20once%20they%20are%20back%20with%20a%20370-plus%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20have%20denied%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20even%20if%20Dr%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%C2%A0%20himself%20turned%20up%20and%20told%20him%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20and%20end%20reservations%2C%20it%20will%20not%20happen.%20His%20call%20for%20over%20400%20seats%20for%20NDA%20was%20meant%20to%20%26quot%3Bdestroy%20the%20conspiracies%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20%26quot%3Bspreading%20lies%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20Constitution.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20yesterday%2C%20he%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20absolute%20majority%20even%20now%2C%20but%20it%20has%20been%20used%20to%20remove%20Article%20370%2C%20abolish%20triple%20talaq.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20can%20end%20reservation%2C%20or%20harm%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20also%20attacked%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20reservations%20--%20a%20sensitive%20topic%20in%20the%20country%20and%20especially%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20where%20a%20chunk%20of%20the%20population%20are%20tribals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20they%20are%20saying%20that%20they%20are%20not%20against%20reservation%3F%20Then%20why%20are%20you%20privatising%20the%20public%20sector%2C%20railways%3F%20Why%20did%20you%20bring%20Agniveer%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20claims%20the%20allegations%20on%20reservation%20and%20Constitution%20change%20are%20the%20Opposition's%20way%20of%20digressing%20from%20their%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcusing%20the%20Congress%20of%20betraying%20Scheduled%20castes%20and%20tribes%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Castes%2C%C2%A0%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20this%20was%20the%20reason%20these%20communities%20have%20%26quot%3Bdistanced%20themselves%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20forced%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20spread%20lies.%20They%20are%20telling%20the%20people%20that%20BJP%20will%20change%20the%20Constitution%20and%20end%20reservations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20yesterday%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Solapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714478640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fukfv63n8_rahul-gandhi-_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-on-constitution-change-reservation-rahul-gandhi-takes-on-amit-shah-5557464%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20attacked%20the%20BJP%20and%20Union%20home%20minster%20Amit%20Shah%20today%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20constitution%20change%20and%20reservations%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bhind.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-on-constitution-change-reservation-rahul-gandhi-takes-on-amit-shah-5557464%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-on-constitution-change-reservation-rahul-gandhi-takes-on-amit-shah-5557464%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-on-constitution-change-reservation-rahul-gandhi-takes-on-amit-shah-5557464%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thousands%20Of%20Passengers%20Stranded%20As%20Australian%20Airline%20Cancels%20All%20Flights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20passengers%20were%20stranded%20across%20Australia%20after%20low-cost%20airline%20Bonza%20abruptly%20cancelled%20all%20flights%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68925711%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20Passengers%20wanting%20to%20fly%20from%20the%20Sunshine%20Coast%2C%20Melbourne%2C%20Gold%20Coast%20and%20Avalon%20arrived%20at%20the%20airports%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20to%20find%20their%20flights%20had%20been%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBonza%20chief%20executive%20Tim%20Jordan%20confirmed%20%EF%BB%BFthe%20airline%20had%20temporarily%20suspended%20services%20amid%20discussions%20regarding%20the%20ongoing%20viability%20of%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20apologise%20to%20our%20customers%20who%20are%20impacted%20by%20this%20and%20we're%20working%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20to%20determine%20a%20way%20forward%20that%20ensures%20there%20is%20ongoing%20competition%20in%20the%20Australian%20domestic%20aviation%20market%2C''%20he%20said%20after%20flights%20were%20cancelled%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdministrator%20Hall%20Chadwick%20said%20%EF%BB%BFthe%20entire%20fleet%20would%20be%20grounded%20up%20to%20and%20including%20Thursday%20this%20week%2C%20as%20key%20parties%20consider%20whether%20the%20company%20can%20continue%20operating%20during%20administration.%20The%20airline%20also%20advised%20travellers%20with%20flights%20booked%20up%20until%20Friday%20morning%20to%20not%20travel%20to%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20voluntary%20administrators%20with%20the%20engagement%20of%20Norton%20Rose%20Fulbright%20are%20currently%20considering%20the%20continued%20trading%20of%20the%20company's%20operations%20during%20the%20administration%20period%20including%20the%20continuation%20of%20employment%20of%20all%20employees%20of%20the%20company.%20The%20discussions%20regarding%20ongoing%20trading%20are%20occurring%20over%20the%20forthcoming%20days%20and%20the%20administrators%20will%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20update%20all%20stakeholders%20as%20the%20matter%20progresses%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20joint%20release%20issued%20by%20Hall%20Chadwick%20and%20Bonza%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Csection%20data-component%3D%5C%22text-block%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBonza%20launched%20in%202023%20and%20operated%20a%20range%20of%20domestic%20flights%20across%20eastern%20Australia.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20has%20struggled%20with%20aircraft%20shortages%20and%20low%20patronage%20since%20its%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECatherine%20King%2C%20Australia's%20transportation%20minister%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20she%20had%20spoken%20with%20representatives%20from%20Bonza%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20keep%20passengers%20fully%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20have%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20to%20Bonza%20that%20we%20expect%20that%20they%20inform%20passengers%20about%20what%20their%20options%20are%2C%20what%20changes%20are%20being%20made%2C%20and%20that%20they%20respect%20their%20consumer%20rights%2C%20of%20which%20they%20do%20have%20some.%20Our%20focus%20right%20at%20the%20moment%20is%20to%20assist%20Australian%20passengers%20who%20are%20stranded%20at%20the%20end%20of%20school%20holidays%2C''%20Ms%20King%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Csection%20data-component%3D%5C%22text-block%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20main%20transport%20union%20is%20now%20seeking%20an%20urgent%20meeting%20with%20the%20airline's%20leadership%20to%20discuss%20how%20the%20sudden%20closure%20will%20impact%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fsection%3E%5Cn%3Csection%20data-component%3D%5C%22text-block%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBonza%20must%20ensure%20staff%20are%20prioritised%20and%20informed%20as%20this%20process%20plays%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20national%20secretary%20of%20the%20transport%20workers%20union%2C