ginID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68927263%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20animated%20version%20of%20the%20Manchester%20City%20footballer%20will%20become%20the%20Barbarian%20King%20in%20the%20game.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68927263%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68927263.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68927263.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AstraZeneca%20Admits%20Covishield%20Jab%20Has%20Rare%20Side-Effect.%20Should%20You%20Worry%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThrombosis%20Thrombocytopenia%20Syndrome%20(TTS)%20--%20a%20blood%20clot%20disorder%20--%20is%20a%20rare%20side%20effect%20of%20AstraZeneca's%20Covid%20vaccine%2C%20and%20the%20risks%20far%20outweigh%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20jab%2C%20doctors%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20reports%20said%20that%20AstraZeneca%20has%20for%20the%20first%20time%20accepted%20in%20court%20documents%20that%20its%20vaccine%2C%20developed%20in%20partnership%20with%20Oxford%20University%2C%20can%20raise%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20rare%20and%20serious%20blood%20clot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Oxford-AstraZeneca%20Covid%20vaccine%2C%20sold%20as%20Covishield%20in%20India%20and%20Vaxzevria%20in%20Europe%20is%20a%20viral%20vector%20vaccine%20developed%20using%20the%20modified%20chimpanzee%20adenovirus%20ChAdOx1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECovishield%20manufactured%20and%20marketed%20in%20India%20in%20partnership%20with%20Serum%20Institute%20of%20India%20(SII)%2C%20was%20widely%20administered%20in%20the%20country%20--%20to%20almost%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Indian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrombotic%20Thrombocytopenic%20Syndrome%20(TTS)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20rare%20but%20very%20serious%20adverse%20effects%20that%20has%20happened%20as%20part%20of%20Vaccine-induced%20Immune%20Thrombotic%20Thrombocytopenic%20Purpura%20(VITTP).%20The%20incidence%20has%20been%20as%20low%20as%20one%20in%2050%2C000%20(0.002%20per%20cent)%2C%20but%20in%20a%20huge%20population%2C%20the%20number%20becomes%20sizeable%2C%26quot%3B%20infectious%20disease%20expert%20Dr.%20Ishwar%20Gilada%2C%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTTS%20is%20a%20very%20rare%20condition%20resulting%20from%20an%20abnormal%20immune%20response.%20Although%20it%20has%20several%20causes%2C%20it%20has%20also%20been%20linked%20with%20adenovirus%20vector%20vaccines%20and%20the%20WHO%20published%20a%20report%20on%20May%2027%2C%202021%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Rajeev%20Jayadevan%2C%20co-chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association's%20National%20Covid-19%20Task%20Force%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20the%20case%3F%20The%20British-Swedish%20multinational%20pharmaceutical%20company%20has%20admitted%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20UK%20court%20documents%20that%20its%20Covid%20vaccine%20can%20cause%20a%20rare%20blood%20clot%20risk%2C%20the%20Telegraph%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2051%20cases%20have%20been%20lodged%20in%20the%20UK%20High%20Court%20against%20the%20pharmaceutical%20giant%20over%20claims%20that%20its%20Covid%20vaccine%20caused%20death%20and%20serious%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20and%20grieving%20relatives%20have%20sought%20damages%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20up%20to%20100%20million%20pounds%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20AstraZeneca%20is%20contesting%20the%20claims%20%26quot%3Bit%20has%20accepted%2C%20in%20a%20legal%20document%20submitted%20to%20the%20High%20Court%20in%20February%20that%20its%20Covid%20vaccine%20'can%2C%20in%20very%20rare%20cases%2C%20cause%20TTS'%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETTS%20causes%20people%20to%20have%20blood%20clots%20and%20a%20low%20blood%20platelet%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstraZeneca's%20Covid%20vaccine%20and%20link%20to%20TTS%3F%20In%20India%2C%20almost%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20people%20who%20received%20Covid%20vaccine%2C%20received%20the%20AstraZeneca%20vaccine%20which%20in%20India%20is%20called%20Covishield.%20It%20is%20made%20from%20a%20harmless%20cold%20virus%2C%20which%20is%20from%20chimpanzees%20and%20it%20is%20called%20adenovirus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20this%20virus%20is%20genetically%20modified%20or%20engineered%20to%20match%20the%20SARS-CoV-2%2C%20a%20causative%20organism%20for%20Covid-19%2C%20this%20works%20on%20a%20spike%20protein.%20So%2C%20the%20vaccine%20is%20incorporated%20with%20the%20S%20spike%20protein%20genetic%20sequence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr.%20Ishwar%2C%20Secretary%20General%20People's%20Health%20Organisation-India%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20mechanism%20of%20potential%20TTS%20risk%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20vaccine%20is%20injected%20in%20the%20arm%20which%20is%20in%20the%20deltoid%20muscle.%20However%2C%20%26quot%3Bsometimes%20instead%20of%20just%20getting%20into%20muscles%2C%20it%20also%20enters%20the%20bloodstream.%20Once%20it%20enters%20the%20bloodstream%2C%20the%20adenovirus%20in%20the%20vaccines%20acts%20like%20a%20magnet%2C%20with%20a%20special%20affinity%20to%20a%20type%20of%20protein%20in%20the%20blood%20called%20platelet%20factor%204%20(PF4)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20PF4%20is%20normally%20used%20by%20the%20body%20to%20promote%20coagulation%20in%20blood%2C%20in%20rare%20instances%2C%20the%20body's%20immune%20system%20confuses%20it%20as%20a%20foreign%20body%20or%20foreign%20invader%20and%20then%20releases%20antibodies%20to%20attack%20it%20--%20called%20mistaken%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20theorised%20that%20such%20antibodies%20then%20react%20and%20clump%20together%20with%20PF4%2C%20forming%20the%20blood%20clots%20that%20have%20become%20so%20heavily%20linked%20with%20the%20vaccine.%20Such%20clots%20in%20the%20brain%20and%20heart%20can%20cause%20disastrous%20adverse%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20all%20Covishield%20vaccine%20takers%20be%20worried%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20we%20need%20not%20because%20it%20has%20happened%20to%20a%20very%20few%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Ishwar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20difficulty%20is%20to%20distinguish%20between%20the%20complications%20that%20are%20caused%20by%20Covid%20itself%20or%20long-Covid%20or%20the%20vaccine.%20That%20remains%20debatable%20and%20indistinguishable%20for%20the%20scientific%20community%20as%20also%20the%20legal%20fraternity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20Dr.%20Rajeev%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20are%20vaccinated%20have%20an%20overall%20lower%20risk%20of%20death%20from%20Covid%20as%20well%20as%20complications%20such%20as%20post-Covid%20heart%20attacks%20and%20strokes%20afterward%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20there%20are%20extremely%20rare%20serious%20side%20effects%20for%20vaccines%2C%20the%20benefits%20far%20outweigh%20the%20risks.%20Covid%20vaccines%20have%20prevented%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20from%20dying.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20the%20US%2C%20232%2C000-318%2C000%20people%20have%20died%20from%20Covid%2C%20due%20to%20refusal%20to%20vaccinate%20from%20disproportionate%20fear%20of%20vaccination%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714477980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-12%2Fi68utsbg_astrazeneca-vaccine_625x300_30_December_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fastrazeneca-admits-covishield-jab-has-rare-side-effect-should