%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20%26quot%3Bbadge%20in%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20security%20officer%20took%20his%20badge%20and%20told%20him%20he%20was%20laid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7186490099612704768%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221565%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesla%20timeline%3A%2007%2F22%2F2019%20-%2004%2F15%2F2024.%20About%205%20years%20at%20Tesla.%20Half%20a%20decade!.%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20Mr%20Murillo%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20one%20point%20in%202023%20I%20was%20even%20sacrificing%20sleeping%20in%20my%20car%20on%20work%20days%20just%20to%20avoid%20commuting%20to%20work.%20Showered%20at%20the%20factory%20and%20slept%20in%20the%20parking%20lot.%20Microwaved%20dinner%20in%20the%20break%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2029-year-old%20said%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bsacrificed%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20company%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20a%20small%20part%20of%20a%20chapter%20that%20is%20ending%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20whole%20book%20waiting%20to%20be%20written.%20I'm%20only%2029%20years%20old%20and%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20career%20time%20in%20me.%20I%20went%20from%20Production%20Associate%2C%20to%20Lead%20Production%20Associate%2C%20to%20being%20a%20Production%20Supervisor.%20Starting%20from%20the%20very%20bottom%20and%20worked%20my%20way%20up.%20Learned%20a%20lot%20of%20adapting%20to%20the%20ever-changing%20environment%2C%20to%20working%20with%20less%20but%20getting%20more%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Murillo%20also%20remembered%20his%20supervisor%20Louie%20Afusia%20who%20taught%20him%20about%20%26quot%3Bdelegating%2C%20following%20up%2C%20and%20finishing%20through.%26quot%3B%20The%20former%20Tesla%20employee%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20used%20to%20tell%20me%3A%20'listen%20to%20the%20people%2C%20not%20against%20them.'%20I%20even%20played%20semi%20pro%20football%20with%20him%20one%20Spring%20season.%20But%20he%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20about%20leadership%2C%20and%20i'm%20glad%20to%20have%20met%20him%20in%20my%20career%20at%20Tesla.%20He%20was%20this%20huge%20Somoan%20USO%2C%20that%20had%20a%20good%20heart.%20Louie%20passed%20away%20in%2002%2F2023.%20He's%20gone%2C%20but%20not%20forgotten.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcluding%20the%20post%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20you%20make%20something%20last%20forever%20is%20you%20inspire%20the%20next%20generation%20and%20then%20the%20next.%20Always%20leave%20the%20place%20better%20than%20you%20found%20it.%20One%20thing%20Tony%20Stark%20(Ironman)%20said%20in%20the%20movie%20Avengers%20Endgame%3A%20'Part%20of%20the%20journey%20is%20the%20end'.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5CnSince%20being%20shared%2C%20his%20post%20has%20amassed%20a%20lot%20of%20reactions%20from%20internet%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20always%20room%20for%20talents%20and%20who%20knows%2C%20it%20might%20be%20a%20million%20times%20better%20than%20you%20can%20imagine.%20Stay%20strong%20and%20don't%20let%20it%20get%20on%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20you%20have%20wrote%20this%20with%20such%20grace%20and%20strength...wish%20you%20all%20the%20best%20for%20your%20next%20chapter%20of%20the%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BSorry%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20being%20being%20laidoff.%20Amazing%20story%20about%20growth%20and%20development.%20You%20definitely%20have%20so%20much%20time%20to%20build%20your%20career%20from%20this%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20company%20that%20lays%20you%20off%20by%20text%20is%20not%20a%20company%20you%20want%20to%20work%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714477200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F81gjero8_tesla-employee