%20Reddy's%20Party%20Names%20These%20Commoners%20As%20Star%20Campaigners%20For%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPandalaneni%20Sivaprasad.%20Katari%20Jagadish.%20Anantha%20Lakshmi.%20Syed%20Anwar.%20Challa%20Eswari.%20These%20not-so%20familiar%20names%20are%20going%20to%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20spotlight.%20They%20are%20the%20working%20class%20people%20who%20have%20been%20named%20the%20star%20campaigners%20by%20the%20Jagan%20Reddy%20Mohan%20party%20for%20the%20elections%2C%20possibly%20a%20first%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmid%20a%20popular%20trend%20of%20enlisting%20film%20stars%2C%20celebrities%2C%20and%20influencers%20as%20star%20campaigners%20for%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20YSRCP%20has%20chosen%20an%20extraordinary%20path.%20A%20path%20that%20has%20not%20been%20attempted%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country%20before.%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20YSRCP%20President%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20has%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20common%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20his%20'Star%20Campaigners'%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20marking%20a%20historic%20first%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20party%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20submitted%20a%20list%20of%20%26quot%3B12%20commoners%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20designating%20them%20as%20YSRCP's%20official%20'Star%20Campaigners'%20for%20the%20upcoming%20polls%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20will%20represent%20the%20nearly%20five%20crore%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20YSRCP's%20belief%20that%20every%20person%20of%20the%20state%20is%20their%20'Star%20Campaigner.'%20These%20individuals%2C%20hailing%20from%20humble%20backgrounds%2C%20will%20campaign%20for%20the%20party%20on%20ground%20and%20help%20propagate%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy's%20message%20till%20the%20last%20mile%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20said%2C%20aiming%20to%20score%20a%20second%20term.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnOut%20of%20the%2012%20star%20campaigners%2C%204%20are%20homemakers%2C%202%20are%20farmers%2C%201%20is%20an%20auto%20driver%2C%201%20a%20tailor%2C%20and%204%20are%20former%20government%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20while%20campaigning%2C%20Jagan%20Reddy%20called%20the%20common%20people%20his%20star%20campaigners%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20go%20to%20every%20house%20and%20highlight%20the%20good%20things%20done%20by%20his%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20May%2013%20for%20the%20175-member%20Assembly%20and%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20look%20at%20some%20of%20the%20star%20campaigners%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandalaneni%20Sivaprasad%2C%20from%20Avanigadda%20constituency%2C%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20of%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKatari%20Jagadish%2C%20from%20Anakapalli%20constituency%2C%20runs%20a%20small%20roadside%20shop%20sewing%20seat%20covers%20for%20two-wheelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnantha%20Lakshmi%2C%20representing%20Rajahmundry%20City%20Constituency%2C%20works%20at%20a%20clothing%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyed%20Anwar%2C%20Nellore%20Rural%2C%20Nellore%20District%2C%20works%20as%20a%20government%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChalla%20Eswari%2C%20from%20Mylavaram%20Constituency%2C%20works%20as%20a%20YSRCP%20government%20volunteer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandalaneni%20Sivaprasad%2C%20from%20Avanigadda%20constituency%2C%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20of%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714475760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F6ugrnj2k_jagan-reddy-1200-_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagan-mohan-reddys-party-names-commoners-as-star-campaigners-for-polls-5557112%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pandalaneni%20Sivaprasad.%20Katari%20Jagadish.%20Anantha%20Lakshmi.%20Syed%20Anwar.%20Challa%20Eswari