e%20will%20come%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20ordered%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegations%20and%20Karthik%20said%20he%20will%20approach%20the%20team%20with%20documents%20and%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20(for%20distancing%20from%20Mr%20Revanna)%20was%20that%20my%20land%20was%20taken%20away%20and%20my%20wife%20was%20beaten%20up.%20I%20was%20mentally%20tortured.%20Because%20my%20land%20was%20taken%20away%2C%20I%20came%20out%20of%20the%20job%20and%20started%20my%20fight%20(to%20get%20back%20land)%2C%26quot%3B%20Karthik%20said%20in%20the%20message%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20adding%20that%20Mr%20Gowda%20had%20written%20to%20the%20BJP%20brass%20not%20to%20give%20a%20ticket%20to%20Mr%20Revanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Why%20Would%20We%20Release%20Videos%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gowda%20told%20reporters%20that%20Karthik%20had%20been%20seen%20several%20times%20with%20Mr%20Revanna's%20Congress%20rival%20from%20Hassan%20constituency%2C%20Shreyas%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20someone%20benefiting%20from%20this%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Congress.%20Only%20for%20his%20political%20gain%2C%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20(Shreyas%20Patel)%20has%20mortgaged%20the%20modesty%20of%20women%20seen%20in%20the%20videos%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gowda%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20the%20PTI%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20said%20neither%20the%20JDS%20nor%20his%20party%20would%20release%20the%20videos%20as%20doing%20so%20would%20hurt%20the%20NDA%2C%20and%20that%20he%20would%20give%20important%20documents%20to%20the%20SIT%20when%20they%20serve%20him%20a%20notice.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20leaders%20will%20fall%20in%20the%20ditch%20they%20have%20dug%20for%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20Holenarasipura%20police%20station%20against%20Mr%20Revanna%20and%20his%20father%20for%20allegedly%20sexually%20harassing%20their%20former%20cook.%20%C2%A0Karnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Hassan%20MP%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20return%20to%20India%20by%20the%20SIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714473480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Flmmnkp3g_prajwal-revanna_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-sex-scandal-prajwal-revannas-ex-driver-bjp-leader-accuse-each-other-of-leaking-videos-5556892%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20controversy%20over%20the%20alleged%20sex%20scandal%20involving%20Hassan%20MP%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20has%20escalated%20with%20his%20former%20driver%20and%20a%20BJP%20leader%20accusing%20each%20other%20of%20leaking%20the%20videos%20in%20which%20he%20can%20allegedly%20be%20seen%20sexually%20assaulting%20multiple%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-sex-scandal-prajwal-revannas-ex-driver-bjp-leader-accuse-each-other-of-leaking-videos-5556892%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-sex-scandal-prajwal-revannas-ex-driver-bjp-leader-accuse-each-other-of-leaking-videos-5556892%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-sex-scandal-prajwal-revannas-ex-driver-bjp-leader-accuse-each-other-of-leaking-videos-5556892%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maldivians%20and%20Indians%20clash%20in%20Male%2C%202%20injured%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714473415000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109727066%2Cimgsize-1110564.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.co