for%20a%20very%20compelling%20read%2C%20Siddarth%20Saikia%2C%20the%20owner%20and%20manager%20of%20affairs%20at%20the%20homestay%2C%20says%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20piece%20of%20fiction%3B%20the%20safe%20exists.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20key%20is%20lost%20in%20time%2C%20and%20the%20safe%E2%80%99s%20outer%20frame%20bears%20many%20markings.%20Many%20have%20tried%20to%20prise%20it%20open%20to%20check%20what%20it%20contains%2C%20but%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20budge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20professional%20locksmith%2C%20who%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20through%2C%20informed%20Siddarth%20and%20the%20family%20that%20the%20safe%E2%80%99s%20rusted%20interiors%20and%20strategic%20position%20within%20the%20wall%20meant%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20crack%20it%20open%20would%20be%20to%20break%20down%20the%20wall%20itself.%20And%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20resort%20to%20this%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20to%20this%20day%2C%20the%20safe%20lies%20untouched%20by%20the%20fingers%20of%20time%2C%20holding%20within%20it%20many%20mysteries%20and%20adding%20its%20own%20little%20bit%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344999%2Fhomestay-in-panchgani-roadtrip-from-mumbai-sustainable-organic-food-solar-panel-long-weekend-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintrigue%20to%20the%20property%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20attractive%20as%20it%20is%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20draw%20at%20the%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20homestay%20helmed%20by%20a%20mother-son%20duo%20from%20Delhi.%20The%20vibrant%20yellows%20of%20the%20bungalow%20are%20a%20sight%20for%20sore%20eyes%2C%20its%20layout%20offering%20pockets%20of%20unexpected%20calm%20to%20the%20weary%20traveller%20or%20to%20anyone%20who%20comes%20looking%20for%20some%20peace%20and%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWould%20you%20believe%20it%20if%20you%20were%20told%20that%20not%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20th